      <title>南歌子</title>
      <link href="posts/3746816291.html"/>
      <url>posts/3746816291.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<div style="max-width: 600px;margin: 0 auto; padding: 30px;">    <center style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 1.6rem;margin-bottom: 20px;">其一</center>    <p style="text-indent: 2em;font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 2rem;">一曲催人叹，千年几度重。流光杯盏绕帘栊，声散忽惊昔事已成空。</p>    <p style="text-indent: 2em;font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 2rem;">乍暖风难静，怜花遍地红。浮生何必怨相逢，无可觅时又恨梦匆匆。</p>    <center style="font-weight: bold;font-size: 1.6rem;margin-bottom: 20px;">其二</center>    <p style="text-indent: 2em;font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 2rem;">霞散随风远，寒天映日红。昔年锦瑟话愁浓，终是别时归处又相逢。</p>    <p style="text-indent: 2em;font-size: 1.3rem; line-height: 2rem;">曾恐情难定，如今淡月胧。人之于世自缘成，一梦红楼缘尽各西东。</p></div>]]></content>
      
      
